               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17630706-7-off36-c73" targOrder="Y" targets="t17630706-7-defend87 t17630706-7-off36 t17630706-7-verdict38"></join>
         
               <p>266, 267. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17630706-7-defend85" type="defendantName">
                     William 
                     Morgan 
                  <interp inst="t17630706-7-defend85" type="surname" value="Morgan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-defend85" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-defend85" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
                
             and 
               
                  <persName id="t17630706-7-defend87" type="defendantName">
                     John 
                     Forrester 
                  <interp inst="t17630706-7-defend87" type="surname" value="Forrester"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-defend87" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-defend87" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
                
             were indicted for <rs id="t17630706-7-off36" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-off36" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-off36" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing two pair of chrystal sleeve-buttons set in silver, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17630706-7-victim89" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Simpson 
                  <interp inst="t17630706-7-victim89" type="surname" value="Simpson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-victim89" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-victim89" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17630706-7-off36 t17630706-7-victim89"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17630706-7-cd37" type="crimeDate">June 20</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17630706-7-off36 t17630706-7-cd37"></join>. *</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17630706-7-person90">
                  George 
                  Simpson 
               <interp inst="t17630706-7-person90" type="surname" value="Simpson"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-person90" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-person90" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             deposed, Forrester came into his shop on the 20th of June, and the other followed immediately; he asked for a pair of sleeve-buttons, they were shewed some of half a crown, at 5 s. and at 3 s. 6 d. He missed a pair at 3 s. 6 d. being asked for them, they denied having them, but when going to send for an officer, Morgan delivered them out of his hand two pair and a half; and that Morgan offered him his silver watch to indemnify him, that he should not be prosecuted for compounding a felony, if he would let them go.</p>
               <p>Both <rs id="t17630706-7-verdict38" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-verdict38" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17630706-7-punish39" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17630706-7-punish39" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17630706-7-defend85 t17630706-7-punish39"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17630706-7-defend87 t17630706-7-punish39"></join>
               T
            </rs>.</p>
